OL,3,CRise in school exclusions due to
OL,4,Cketamine use
OL,6,FMore and more students are being
OL,7,Fsuspended and excluded due to ketamine
OL,8,Fusage, a report has found.
OL,10,FAccording to the report from Halton
OL,11,FBorough Council, 24 students were
OL,12,Fsuspended from schools in Halton
OL,13,Flinked to ketamine and 12 were
OL,14,Fpermanently excluded during the 2024/
OL,15,F25 school year.
OL,17,FThis was a huge rise from the year
OL,18,Fbefore when just one student was
OL,19,Fsuspended and two were permanently
OL,20,Fexcluded.
