OL,3,CRise in school exclusions due to
OL,4,Cketamine use
OL,6,FAfter such a large increase, police
OL,7,Fhave been working with The Bridge
OL,8,FSchool Pupil Referral Unit to carry
OL,9,Fout targeted operations and raids
OL,10,Fleading to a number of arrests.
OL,12,FAwareness of the dangers of ketamine
OL,13,Fhas also been embedded into school
OL,14,Fsafeguarding training.
OL,16,FSince these measures were introduced
OL,17,Fat the start of the school year in
OL,18,FSeptember 2025, the number of pupils
OL,19,Ffacing exclusion has dropped.
