OL,3,CRise in school exclusions due to
OL,4,Cketamine use
OL,6,F"Continued use without effective
OL,7,Fprevention threatens attendance,
OL,8,Fattainment, and educational stability
OL,9,Ffor affected young people," the report
OL,10,Fsays.
OL,12,FThe report highlighting Halton's
OL,13,Fresponse to rising ketamine use says
OL,14,Fthat Children and Young People
OL,15,Fservices are supporting 43 young
OL,16,Fpeople, including 20 with ketamine as
OL,17,Ftheir primary drug.
