OL,6,FIt says that: "Demand and the
OL,7,Fcomparatively high cost of ketamine
OL,8,Fdetox in young adults has
OL,9,Fsignificantly contributed to an
OL,10,Fadditional pressure of #170,000 on
OL,11,Fpublic health budgets in 2025/26."
OL,13,FThe report also notes that more young
OL,14,Fwomen are making up a significant
OL,15,Fproportion of those harmed by
OL,16,Fketamine, which is not typical for
OL,17,Fdrug misuse.
