OL,3,CRise in school exclusions due to
OL,4,Cketamine use
OL,6,FChief Inspector Amber Hodson, Cheshire
OL,7,FPolice's Drug Lead, said: "We are
OL,8,Fextremely concerned by the rise in
OL,9,Fketamine-related harm. Behind every
OL,10,Fstatistic is a person whose health,
OL,11,Flife opportunities and safety are
OL,12,Fbeing put at risk.
OL,14,F"We're seeing the damage ketamine is
OL,15,Fdoing first-hand with some people
OL,16,Fcoming into custody with bladder
OL,17,Fissues so serious that they've had to
OL,18,Fwear nappies ` a stark reminder of how
OL,19,Fdangerous this drug really is.
