OL,6,F"We're determined to take ketamine off
OL,7,Fthe streets of Cheshire, and we need
OL,8,Fthe public's help to target the
OL,9,Findividuals bringing this drug into
OL,10,Four communities and exploiting
OL,11,Fvulnerable young people to do it."
OL,13,FKetamine is considered a Class B drug
OL,14,Fbut the UK government is currently
OL,15,Fseeking advice from the Advisory
OL,16,FCouncil on the Misuse of Drugs (ACMD)
OL,17,Fon whether it should be reclassified
OL,18,Fto a Class A drug.
